Titolo: Phantom 2040 (video game)

Anno: 1995

Descrizione: Phantom 2040 is an action-adventure platform game developed by Hearst Entertainment and published by Viacom New Media in 1995 for the Genesis, Super NES and Game Gear. The game is directly based upon the animated television series Phantom 2040 but follows a plotline not strictly taken by the show. The game plays similarly to the Metroid and Castlevania series.

Genere: Action-adventure 

Valutazione: N/A
